# Summary
This documentation page details the Snapchat Ads integration with Amplitude, which allows users to send audience cohorts from Amplitude to Snapchat Ads for targeted advertising campaigns, requiring specific user properties (Email, Phone Number, or Mobile Ad ID) with SHA256 encryption and explaining the setup process in both platforms.

